Module photos

Package com.photos.fxml

package com.photos.fxml
Contains controllers/dialogs/components for the UI of the application. The "view"/"controller" layer, so to speak.
  • Related Packages

    Description

    Contains the models representing concrete entities in the application, e.g User and Photo.
    com.photos.utility
    Contains utility classes not associated with any particular user, model, or controller.
